ADD.FAILED: Hey! You need to wait for options to show before hitting enter. You entered "{{categoryId}}" which isn't a category here.
ADD.INVALID: I failed to find that category! Try again.

CATEGORY.ROLES_EMPTY: Hey! For some reason I don't see any react roles in that category. If this issues persist please report it to the support server.
CATEGORY.ROLES_MAX: Hey! Category {{categoryName}}` already has the max of 20 react roles. This is due to Discords reaction limitation. Make another category!

REACT_ROLE.FIND_FAILED: Failed to find the react role!
REACT_ROLE.EXISTING: Hey! This role is already in the category `{{categoryName}}`.
REACT_ROLE.ADD_MORE: I've added `{{reactRoleName}}` to `{{categoryName}}`, you can add more roles if you wish.
REACT_ROLE.NO_MORE: I've added `{{reactRoleName}}` to `{{categoryName}}`. If you want to add more you need to create more react roles first.
REACT_ROLE.UPDATE_FAILED: Hey! I had an issue adding `{{reactRoleName}}` to the category `{{categoryName}}`. Please wait a second and try again.
REACT_ROLE.EMPTY: You should create a few react roles first! Check out `/react-role`!

BUTTON.ADD: Below are reaction roles and their respective emojis. Click the buttons you want to add to the category `{{categoryName}}`.
BUTTON.FAIL:
Hey! I had an issue making some buttons for you. Sometimes emojis aren't supported, like iPhone emojis, please make sure to use Discords emoji picker.
If the problem persist please visit the support server found in the `/info` command so we can figure out the issue!

CREATE.SUCCESS: Hey! I successfully created the category `{{name}}` for you!
CREATE.FAILED: Hey! I had some trouble creating that category for you. Please wait a minute and try again.

CATEGORY.INVALID_NAME: Hey! It says you submitted no category name! You need to submit that. Please try again.
CATEGORY.MAX_NAME_LENGTH: Hey! Discord only allows 100 characters max for their embed titles. Try making the category name simple and make the rest the category description!
CATEGORY.EXIST: Hey! It turns out you already have a category with that name made. Try checking it out.

EDIT.SUCCESS: Hey! I successfully updated the category `{{name}}` for you.
EDIT.FAILED: Hey! I couldn't update the category `{{name}}` for you.
EDIT.INVALID: Hey! You need to pass at _least_ one updated field about the category.

CATEGORY.INVALID_ID: I couldn't find the category from the command. Please try again.
CATEGORY.INVALID: Hey! I couldn't find the category. Please wait a second and try again.

LIST.EMPTY: Hey! It appears that there aren't any categories for this server, go make some with `/category-create`!
LIST.PROLONG:
Hey! Let me build those embeds for you.

If you notice any react roles that have deleted roles run `/react-clean` to remove them.

REMOVE.SUCCESS: Hey! I successfully deleted the category `{{name}}` for you and freed all the roles on it.
REMOVE.FAILED: Hey! I had an issue deleting the category. Please wait a second and try again.

CATEGORY.INVALID: Hey! This is unusual, I couldn't find that category! Please try again after waiting a second.

UPDATE.SUCCESS: Hey! I've successfully re-reacted to the message for you.
UPDATE.EMPTY:
Hey! I see that message uses category `{{name}}` but it has no react roles in it.
Add some react roles to the category with `/category-add` and then try update again. Otherwise just delete it!

INVALID.LINK: Make sure to pass the message link by right click copying it on desktop!
INVALID.CHANNEL: Hey! I couldn't find that channel, make sure you're copying the message link right.
INVALID.MESSAGE: Hey! I looked and didn't see any react roles saved that are associated with that message.
INVALID.CATEGORY: Hey! I couldn't find a category associated with that message.

BUTTON.SUCCESS: Hey! I updated that embed for you.
BUTTON.FAILED: Hey! I couldn't edit the embed, am I missing READ HISTORY / MANAGE MESSAGE permissions?

INVALID.MESSAGE: Hey! I can only edit embeds and buttons that are MY message! Make sure the message you're copying is correct.

REACT.SUCCESS: Hey! I updated the react role embed message related to this category.
